uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.pia.modeller.protein.inference

Class ReportAllInference

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.pia.modeller.protein.inference.AbstractProteinInference
      • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.pia.modeller.protein.inference.ReportAllInference

  • public class ReportAllInference
extends AbstractProteinInference
    This inference reports all the PIA IntermediateGroups as one protein.

    This is similar to distinguish proteins simply by their peptides and report every possible set and subset.

    Author:
    julian
